item.title: About
item.description: Hi there! I am Dhanshree, aka Dee. I love creating things and optimizing them for maximum efficiency. I love solving problems - whether they’re rooted in Code, or in the kitchen. And yes, I love to cook (and eat, duh!). I also work as a Data Scientist at a legal tech startup in Bangalore where I work on cool NLP stuff with an amazing team. Ciao!
